{"tid":2009720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［12/2019］華春瑩：911事件殷鑒不遠，美方不要好了傷疤忘了痛","createTime":"2020-05-10T03:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T03:36:24.000Z","uid":200758,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2fda4877ce1696d20517ac5c65a9a14eea4ec112","tid":2009720,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"中國外交部發言人華春瑩在4日舉行的例行記者會上表示，近年來，美國打著人權、反恐的旗號在阿富汗、伊拉克、敘利亞等地燃起戰火，發動戰爭，導致數百萬無辜民眾傷亡，大量難民流離失所。<br />\n<br />\n她說，美方這種完全蔑視其他國家人民生命和發展權利的行為，激起了全世界有良知人的憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩強調說，恐怖主義、極端主義是人類社會的共同敵人，反恐和去極端化是國際社會的共同責任。「9&middot;11」事件殷鑒不遠，美方不要好了傷疤忘了痛。<br />\n<br />\n如果美方在反恐問題上繼續玩弄雙重標準，甚至妄圖以此來侵害別國的主權和安全，最後只會自食其果，損害美國自身的利益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/gn/2019/12-04/9025179.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.chinanews.com%2Fwap%2Fdetail%2Fzw%2Fgn%2F2019%2F12-04%2F9025179.shtml&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=0352d32a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/gn/2019/12-04/9025179.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"4a271a47af0d07e41221cde1a395d6bee0343839","tid":2009720,"uid":114027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:18:19.000Z","msg":"想恐襲美國再來1次911？"},{"pid":"e0a46af147827f983b65e68a4af956a68469b111","tid":2009720,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:18:50.000Z","msg":"聽落去咁似想恐嚇美國嘅？<br />\n支那想搞個911 2.0出嚟畀美國？"},{"pid":"b4dff2fee11543f67b6ec84039e07bcbe29b11a4","tid":2009720,"uid":214173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"懷疑中共先係911既幕後主謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f902fd12c2d89b4847d4efff6967c48e0e69011","tid":2009720,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"想宣戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df00b6b7e08b09cc69f42493036